cid": 762293, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 158683, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "本质上还是不一样，最起码人的基本权利还是在得到保障", "timestamp": 1608737558, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 762294, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 158683, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "马原只出了这一点的", "timestamp": 1608737568, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 762297, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 158683, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 开玩笑的，相信洞主可以保3.6争4.0", "timestamp": 1608737594, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 762305, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 158683, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 您这叫“人性论历史观”，是“唯心历史观”的一种...马克思主义坚持唯物历史观，这边建议您重修一遍", "timestamp": 1608737664, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 762312, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 158683, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "奴隶和工人没有属于自己的生产资料，不过工人相较奴隶至少具有有限的自由（辞职的自由），而在资本主义国家的视角，为了规避经济危机，工人的利益也是要有基本的保障的", "timestamp": 1608737736, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 762325, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 158683, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "奴隶对奴隶主的人身依附，工人对资本家的人身依附，有相似之处", "timestamp": 1608737840, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 762331, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 158683, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 从马哲出发批判的话，从人性出发只负责解释历史，没有办法看到改变历史的因素。比如您怎么解释对社会弱者的普遍关怀和福利...", "timestamp": 1608737864, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 762350, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 158683, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/MAM0iZcc1QIH82MhPW4UbQ\n一篇文章，可以看看", "timestamp": 1608738001, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 762377, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 158683, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 我马原学的确实不好，不过重修还是算了", "timestamp": 1608738150, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 762380, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 158683, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 您字也感觉怪怪的，你对我个人好像有意见一样", "timestamp": 1608738183, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 762386, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 158683, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 嗯嗯，记下来了", "timestamp": 1608738214, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 7, "pid": 158683, "reply": 20, "tag": null, "text": "深夜复习马原顿悟：工人本质上不就是被剥削的奴隶吗？只不过与古代奴隶相比，有了更多的权利罢了。基因是自私的，社会上总会有一部分人剥削大多数人的生产和生命！或许几千年后回看，21世纪也只不过是进化的奴隶社会吧", "timestamp": 1608737151, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1608738213, "url": "", "vote": {}}}